<h3>Daily Water-Level Percentiles by Month &ndash; Email Alert</h3>
<p>An email notification informs stakeholders when current water levels reach specified elevations at one or more gages or tree islands. An alert is triggered for a gage when the water-level elevation equals or exceeds the 90th percentile water level for the <a href="http://www.saj.usace.army.mil/Portals/44/docs/Planning/EnvironmentalBranch/EnvironmentalDocs/IOP_02_SEIS_37.pdf">Interim Operational Plan (IOP)</a> period. An additional alert is triggered for tree islands when the water level equals or exceeds the maximum tree island ground elevation or when the water level equals or exceeds the 90th percentile for the month for the <abbr title='Interim Operational Plan'>IOP</abbr> period.</p>
<p><strong>To sign up for this email alert system,</strong> please <a href="mailto:bmccloskey@usgs.gov">contact us</a>.</p>
